{"componentChunkName":"component---src-template-post-tsx","path":"/etc/tune-hhkb-bt/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"siteUrl":"https://akasai.space","comment":{"giscus":"akasai/akasai.github.io","repo_id":"MDEwOlJlcG9zaXRvcnkyOTMzMTQ4NzA=","category_id":"DIC_kwDOEXuhNs4CAnjz"}}},"post":{"id":"7dd02f2e-a7f7-500f-9dd0-aba5d47cd80e","excerpt":"해피해킹(HHKB)키보드를 쓴지도 3년 정도 되었습니다. Lindy…","timeToRead":2,"html":"<p>해피해킹(<strong>HHKB</strong>)키보드를 쓴지도 3년 정도 되었습니다.</p>\n<p>Lindy케이블을 연결하여 매우 만족스럽게 사용하고 있었지만, 있었지만 선이 좀 거추장스러워서\n블루투스 지원 키보드 구매를 고려하고 있었습니다.</p>\n<p>우연히 <strong>블루투스</strong> 튜닝에 대한 내용을 알게되어 직접 튜닝을 해보았습니다.</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"준비물-구매\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%A4%80%EB%B9%84%EB%AC%BC-%EA%B5%AC%EB%A7%A4\" aria-label=\"준비물 구매 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>준비물 구매</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://kbdfans.com/products/hhkb-ble-mod-upgrade-module\">블루투스 기판</a></p>\n<p>해피해킹 블루투스 연동 <code class=\"language-text\">기판</code>은 위 사이트에서 구매하였습니다.</p>\n<p>배송은 일주일정도 걸렸던 것 같습니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1200px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 44.99999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"hhkb1\"\n        title=\"hhkb1\"\n        src=\"/static/3c3101ff05fe00c80c11f31df5c8588f/e5166/hhkb1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/3c3101ff05fe00c80c11f31df5c8588f/f93b5/hhkb1.jpg 300w,\n/static/3c3101ff05fe00c80c11f31df5c8588f/b4294/hhkb1.jpg 600w,\n/static/3c3101ff05fe00c80c11f31df5c8588f/e5166/hhkb1.jpg 1200w,\n/static/3c3101ff05fe00c80c11f31df5c8588f/d9c39/hhkb1.jpg 1800w,\n/static/3c3101ff05fe00c80c11f31df5c8588f/df51d/hhkb1.jpg 2400w,\n/static/3c3101ff05fe00c80c11f31df5c8588f/93719/hhkb1.jpg 4000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://ko.aliexpress.com/item/4000032162701.html\">리튬-이온 배터리</a></p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">리튬 이온 배터리</code>는 국내에서도 구할 수 있었는데, 크기나 용량이 다 애매했습니다.</p>\n<p>최소 <strong>3000mAh</strong>이상의 용량을 추천하지만, 두께가 너무 두꺼웠습니다.</p>\n<p>어쩔 수 없이 알리익스프레스에서 구매하였습니다.\n배송이 오래걸린다는 소문이 많아서 걱정했지만, 2주정도 걸린 것 같습니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1200px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 44.99999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"hhkb2\"\n        title=\"hhkb2\"\n        src=\"/static/6f4e3029ace8670dcc7f0769bc87876e/e5166/hhkb2.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/6f4e3029ace8670dcc7f0769bc87876e/f93b5/hhkb2.jpg 300w,\n/static/6f4e3029ace8670dcc7f0769bc87876e/b4294/hhkb2.jpg 600w,\n/static/6f4e3029ace8670dcc7f0769bc87876e/e5166/hhkb2.jpg 1200w,\n/static/6f4e3029ace8670dcc7f0769bc87876e/d9c39/hhkb2.jpg 1800w,\n/static/6f4e3029ace8670dcc7f0769bc87876e/df51d/hhkb2.jpg 2400w,\n/static/6f4e3029ace8670dcc7f0769bc87876e/93719/hhkb2.jpg 4000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h2 id=\"튜닝하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%8A%9C%EB%8B%9D%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"튜닝하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>튜닝하기</h2>\n<p>실패하면 어쩌나 조금 걱정됬지만, 제품들이 도착하고 바로 튜닝을 시작했습니다.</p>\n<p>기존 기판을 분리하고 새 기판을 세팅해줍니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1200px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 44.99999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"hhkb3\"\n        title=\"hhkb3\"\n        src=\"/static/4e53eb4d2a1b316b129536be3e07f44e/e5166/hhkb3.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/4e53eb4d2a1b316b129536be3e07f44e/f93b5/hhkb3.jpg 300w,\n/static/4e53eb4d2a1b316b129536be3e07f44e/b4294/hhkb3.jpg 600w,\n/static/4e53eb4d2a1b316b129536be3e07f44e/e5166/hhkb3.jpg 1200w,\n/static/4e53eb4d2a1b316b129536be3e07f44e/d9c39/hhkb3.jpg 1800w,\n/static/4e53eb4d2a1b316b129536be3e07f44e/df51d/hhkb3.jpg 2400w,\n/static/4e53eb4d2a1b316b129536be3e07f44e/93719/hhkb3.jpg 4000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>튜닝자체는 크게 어렵지 않았습니다.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">기판분리</code> → <code class=\"language-text\">기판 교체</code> → <code class=\"language-text\">배터리 결합</code> → <code class=\"language-text\">조립</code></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>위 순서대로 진행하면 튜닝은 끝납니다.</p>\n<p>다른 블로그 포스팅들과는 다르게 저에게 배송된 배터리는 피복을 벗겨야 진행이 가능했습니다.</p>\n<p>다이소에서 <strong>열 수축형 튜브</strong>를 구매후 전선을 연결해주었습니다.</p>\n<p>전원 커넥터는 기판에 동봉되어있었습니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1200px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 44.99999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"hhkb4\"\n        title=\"hhkb4\"\n        src=\"/static/826eb4899cc08dac2e060dfd558fbe94/e5166/hhkb4.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/826eb4899cc08dac2e060dfd558fbe94/f93b5/hhkb4.jpg 300w,\n/static/826eb4899cc08dac2e060dfd558fbe94/b4294/hhkb4.jpg 600w,\n/static/826eb4899cc08dac2e060dfd558fbe94/e5166/hhkb4.jpg 1200w,\n/static/826eb4899cc08dac2e060dfd558fbe94/d9c39/hhkb4.jpg 1800w,\n/static/826eb4899cc08dac2e060dfd558fbe94/df51d/hhkb4.jpg 2400w,\n/static/826eb4899cc08dac2e060dfd558fbe94/93719/hhkb4.jpg 4000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1200px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 44.99999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"hhkb5\"\n        title=\"hhkb5\"\n        src=\"/static/9963efa4205a92e989e9ab5c52a13800/e5166/hhkb5.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/9963efa4205a92e989e9ab5c52a13800/f93b5/hhkb5.jpg 300w,\n/static/9963efa4205a92e989e9ab5c52a13800/b4294/hhkb5.jpg 600w,\n/static/9963efa4205a92e989e9ab5c52a13800/e5166/hhkb5.jpg 1200w,\n/static/9963efa4205a92e989e9ab5c52a13800/d9c39/hhkb5.jpg 1800w,\n/static/9963efa4205a92e989e9ab5c52a13800/df51d/hhkb5.jpg 2400w,\n/static/9963efa4205a92e989e9ab5c52a13800/93719/hhkb5.jpg 4000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>조립했던 과정을 역행하면 튜닝은 완료됩니다.</p>\n<p>제 키보드는 검은색이여서 LED 불이 나오지 않지만 흰색 키보드는 불빛이 보인다는 얘기도 들었습니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1200px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66.33333333333333%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"hhkb6\"\n        title=\"hhkb6\"\n        src=\"/static/6c998b2385f1815d8e90adfce1362364/e5166/hhkb6.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/6c998b2385f1815d8e90adfce1362364/f93b5/hhkb6.jpg 300w,\n/static/6c998b2385f1815d8e90adfce1362364/b4294/hhkb6.jpg 600w,\n/static/6c998b2385f1815d8e90adfce1362364/e5166/hhkb6.jpg 1200w,\n/static/6c998b2385f1815d8e90adfce1362364/b17f8/hhkb6.jpg 1600w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h2 id=\"페어링\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%8E%98%EC%96%B4%EB%A7%81\" aria-label=\"페어링 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>페어링</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ydkb.io/\">https://ydkb.io/</a></p>\n<p>위 사이트에서 키맵을 변경해줄 수 있습니다. 개인적으론 기본세팅이 익숙해서 큰 변화는 주지 않았습니다.</p>\n<p>페어링을 하면 아래와 같은 이름으로 페어링이 됩니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 570px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 73.00000000000001%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"hhkb7\"\n        title=\"hhkb7\"\n        src=\"/static/6e5e1001ad5271c1b20484ea9a69264c/432e7/hhkb7.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/6e5e1001ad5271c1b20484ea9a69264c/5a46d/hhkb7.png 300w,\n/static/6e5e1001ad5271c1b20484ea9a69264c/432e7/hhkb7.png 570w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 570px) 100vw, 570px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h2 id=\"마치며\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%A7%88%EC%B9%98%EB%A9%B0\" aria-label=\"마치며 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>마치며</h2>\n<p>해피해킹 BT는 새로 사기는 부담되는 가격이기도 하고 특유의 배꼽나온 디자인 때문에 고민을 많이했습니다.</p>\n<p>하지만 이렇게 튜닝을 하니까 훨씬 더 깔끔한 형태가 나와 매우 만족스러웠습니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 58.00000000000001%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"hhkb8\"\n        title=\"hhkb8\"\n        src=\"/static/9d5207c04ffe3ed0597edd5c0b1e6163/0b533/hhkb8.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/9d5207c04ffe3ed0597edd5c0b1e6163/5a46d/hhkb8.png 300w,\n/static/9d5207c04ffe3ed0597edd5c0b1e6163/0b533/hhkb8.png 500w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 859px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 45.666666666666664%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"hhkb9\"\n        title=\"hhkb9\"\n        src=\"/static/4dae5d9239a31d31d3f6b5412fea28d3/39a20/hhkb9.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/4dae5d9239a31d31d3f6b5412fea28d3/5a46d/hhkb9.png 300w,\n/static/4dae5d9239a31d31d3f6b5412fea28d3/0a47e/hhkb9.png 600w,\n/static/4dae5d9239a31d31d3f6b5412fea28d3/39a20/hhkb9.png 859w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 859px) 100vw, 859px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p><strong>10만원</strong> 미만의 투자로 기존에 사용하던 모델을 그대로 사용할 수 있다는 점도 큰 메리트였습니다.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>3000mAh 기준 100% 완충시 체감상 2주 ~ 3주 정도 무선으로 사용할 수 있었습니다. (하루 10시간 사용)</p>\n<p>충전은 잘 때 선에 연결하고, 자고 일어나면 완충되어 있습니다.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>슬립모드 이후 블루투스 페어링은 시간이 조금 걸립니다. 저는 경우 <code class=\"language-text\">스페이스바</code>를 길게 눌러 연결을 하고 있습니다.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>블루투스 감도는 지연이 전혀 느껴지지 않는 정도로 <strong>양호</strong>했습니다.</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p><img src=\"/7ebc36547bc4927da0a9343ee6219c51/hhkb10.gif\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p><span class=\"em red\">혹시 고려하고 있는 분들이 있다면 강력추천 합니다.</span></p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"reference\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#reference\" aria-label=\"reference permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22